				NARST Makes Website Enhancements 
				The NARST Website (www.narst.org) has been updated and enhanced to include a new service that will allow NARST members to interact directly with the membership database (iMIS).  Please check your email inbox for an email containing your updated username and password to access the members-only area and these new member features.   
			 
